name: MultiPlanetary Inus
public_notice: MultiPlanetary Inus has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. For more information, please visit this post.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
MultiPlanetary INUS - The first ever token that combines P2E with AI to unify the top Meme coin community.

What makes your project unique?
INUS mission is "to make MEME practical." As a token to give Meme a practical application, INUS has chosen to use the P2E game as a vehicle, combined with AI, to provide the market with a second generation Memecoin.

History of your project.


What’s next for your project?
Release P2E games combined with AI

What can your token be used for?
